flowchart TD
    subgraph INGEST["DATA INGESTION"]
        BT([BT Workspace]) -->|manual export| RJSON[raw recipe JSON]
    end

    RJSON --> PROC[Data Processing]

    PROC -->|encode with Qwen3-8B| EIDX[(pgvector index)]
    PROC -->|extract connectors / actions / fields| KVOC[(keyword vocabulary\n~2,000 terms)]

    UQUERY([User query]) --> SIG[Signal Detection]
    KVOC -.->|vocab lookup| SIG

    SIG -->|underscore tokens\nw_kw=2.0  w_emb=1.0| UNDER[ ]
    SIG -->|app names only\nw_kw=1.0  w_emb=2.0| APPS[ ]
    SIG -->|no vocab\nw_kw=0.0  w_emb=1.0| NOVOC[ ]

    UNDER -->|ILIKE AND → OR| KWS[Keyword Search]
    APPS  -->|ILIKE AND → OR| KWS

    UNDER -->|cosine similarity| EMBS[Dense Search]
    APPS  -->|cosine similarity| EMBS
    NOVOC -->|cosine similarity| EMBS

    EIDX -.-> EMBS

    KWS  -->|top k×3| RRF[Weighted RRF Fusion]
    EMBS -->|top k×3| RRF

    RRF --> TOPK([top-k results])
